Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:04.11,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}全世界沉浸在爱恋中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:07.53,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}万道光芒 照亮心房
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:10.87,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}我想了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:15.04,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.83,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}话不投机 有些后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:29.78,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}流下眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:35.11,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}心随着急切的情感变乱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:42.42,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}调整情绪 想知道真实的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.45,0:00:48.17,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}执着于达成目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:51.85,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}重要的事物在不觉间模糊 溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:57.57,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}今天是崭新的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:01:03.00,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}全世界沉浸在爱恋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:06.60,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}万道光芒 照亮心房
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:09.94,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}我想了解一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.08,0:01:14.03,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}说给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:17.66,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}一毫米的距离也觉得遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:20.73,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}匆匆走过的青春岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:25.00,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}不会忘 也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:27.76,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}留下闪耀的一页
